{"tid":735122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有LINK]網上湧現假大學證書　仿真度高　人力顧問、律師亦難辨當假為真","createTime":"2018-07-09T08:38:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T10:04:51.000Z","uid":46328,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"3fb49cdc6d3a85641a089531ed66fcaa6d1f9b4f","tid":735122,"uid":46328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:38:10.000Z","msg":"踏入畢業季節，不少順利畢業的大學生，均會陸續收到俗稱「沙紙」的畢業證書。然而，《香港01》發現內地網站出現林林總總的聲稱可以製作虛假大學證書的網站，標榜匯集一千多所來自世界各地的高中、學士以至博士文憑樣本，當中香港的八大院校亦「榜上有名」。<br />\n<br />\n記者喬裝顧客查詢，有出售假證書的網站叫價高達4,800元人民幣，負責人聲稱：「基本上和真的（證書）完全是一模一樣，直接可以拿真證去做對比」，又指是按客戶的需求訂制，為有需求的朋友提供設計製作服務，強調「沒有冒充任何學校或團體，是把製作的學歷證書當成一件新奇特物品出售給客戶。」<br />\n<br />\n證書仿真度，整體文字編排、用字及格式均與真證書類近，惟紙質、字型、簽名、印章等則有出入，然而連資深人力資源顧問周綺萍，以及港大校友、律師莊耀洸亦未能分辨，以假為真。<br />\n<br />\n香港大學發言人回應指，每年均接獲有關學歷確認的查詢，包括確認畢業證書是否由港大發出，而證書有防偽特徵，過去多年曾揭發過極少數偽造港大畢業證書的個案，並採取適當的行動。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1615151/org/134947b762e0333d7a40bddb036c2248.jpg/3J4D9GYXyrqwdiHsnWj1Nf6CdqABKffDRjqj7kY6o-4?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1615151%2Forg%2F134947b762e0333d7a40bddb036c2248.jpg%2F3J4D9GYXyrqwdiHsnWj1Nf6CdqABKffDRjqj7kY6o-4%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=05f92306&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地網站出現林林總總的聲稱可以代客製證書的網站，《香港01》記者在今年1月至3月期間，先後向兩個內地假證書網站以顧客身份查詢。其中一個名為「學位文憑工廠」的網站，分別上載香港浸會大學、理工大學、科技大學、城市大學、中文大學、香港大學、公開大學等證書範例，同時更有中學會考證書、香港會計師公會認證的證書樣本。<br />\n<br />\n表明非真證書　又指沒違反法律<br />\n<br />\n網站表明，其製作的大學證書並非真實證書，但又自認為沒有違反法律，強調是根據「客戶的需求訂制的，僅為有需求的朋友提供設計製作服務，沒有冒充任何學校或團體，僅是把製作的學歷證書當成一件新奇特物品出售給客戶。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.degreediploma.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.degreediploma.hk%2F&d=GJRuu0le9nCCcQ5n9mq0y4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=11bbd7cc\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.degreediploma.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"16e57515804fb758babe9e74c45ad18e5bac48f1","tid":735122,"uid":46328,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:38:24.000Z","msg":"記者最後以1,200元購入一張虛假2017年香港大學工商管理學士畢業證書，同時借來一張2014年的真港大畢業證書作比較。紙質方面，真證書紙張帶有纖維線條，假證書的背景較單調，沒有纖維線條，同時較真證書厚，印刷質量較差。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1614983/org/9b884903cb6780bcb4dbbf821c0de63c.jpg/d0Ej_Dr-D0wsbd3s3Ypq3VMAEJ7BXTDRFXpAxRV6QMU?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1614983%2Forg%2F9b884903cb6780bcb4dbbf821c0de63c.jpg%2Fd0Ej_Dr-D0wsbd3s3Ypq3VMAEJ7BXTDRFXpAxRV6QMU%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=105ff33e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真港大畢業證書（左）及假港大畢業證書（右）。（王海圖攝）<br />\n<br />\n假證書有疑似徐立之及曾蔭權簽署式樣​<br />\n<br />\n在左下角的大學印章方面，真證書的紅色印章色彩較鮮艷，假證書的色彩較暗啞。然而，假證書的校監、校長的簽署出現極大破綻。假證書是在2017年11月1日「頒發」，當時的校長理應是馬婓森，但根據網上資料對照，假證書竟是由前港大校長徐立之「簽署」，他於2014年已離任。<br />\n<br />\n在校監簽署方面，2017年11月本應由行政長官林鄭月娥擔任校監，惟假證書一欄竟出現疑似「Donald Tsang」簽署式樣；根據郵政署2007年發行的「香港特別行政區成立十週年紀念郵票連首日封」，假證書上的「Donald Tsang」簽署式樣，與時任特首曾蔭權的英文簽署類近。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1615010/org/0e725ef03d1ac0a250e8913f0a9be032.jpg/a_5ORXjknQO3gkI70WVKsg3t9wdP1mMelppf75aaX-8?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1615010%2Forg%2F0e725ef03d1ac0a250e8913f0a9be032.jpg%2Fa_5ORXjknQO3gkI70WVKsg3t9wdP1mMelppf75aaX-8%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=560a8dd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1615008/org/f9942184cbdee562841a736361457517.jpg/RzjrsxgkTHrhW5qgjak40AmFMvih0zw9llzJLZZcyS0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1615008%2Forg%2Ff9942184cbdee562841a736361457517.jpg%2FRzjrsxgkTHrhW5qgjak40AmFMvih0zw9llzJLZZcyS0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=eb1d93ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1615113/org/c237be01269aa8d887934a5ed0ce8fca.jpg/D-FZStCq9EYfGLwWgywZ8CeTydPFXaLlJXV8hSV1fIU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1615113%2Forg%2Fc237be01269aa8d887934a5ed0ce8fca.jpg%2FD-FZStCq9EYfGLwWgywZ8CeTydPFXaLlJXV8hSV1fIU%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=12ba5af5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1615007/org/742fa22c5829e206eac4f8f1f95ae1d8.jpg/jZofIRIcQ0cStmR29H03JXiXZfGf8JjohLDsAYSw7AE?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1615007%2Forg%2F742fa22c5829e206eac4f8f1f95ae1d8.jpg%2FjZofIRIcQ0cStmR29H03JXiXZfGf8JjohLDsAYSw7AE%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=2d4b1e2d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"788f4fce0bf4cf9b162594b448948bc2b6bba496","tid":735122,"uid":46328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:38:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1623392/org/e4bc74ad4bc4bf58c16d569c5066c38a.jpg/e_acOd00PtJKr_tA50iDTn49ne15q_38zyxCRM8sQkQ?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1623392%2Forg%2Fe4bc74ad4bc4bf58c16d569c5066c38a.jpg%2Fe_acOd00PtJKr_tA50iDTn49ne15q_38zyxCRM8sQkQ%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=f96afe6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n資深人力資源顧問周綺萍誤選了假證書為「真」證書，記者告知答案時，她顯得十分驚訝。（王海圖攝）<br />\n<br />\n資深人力顧問錯選假證書：紙質較厚<br />\n<br />\n內地網售虛假港大證書有幾真？記者帶同真假證書，分別找到人力資源顧問及律師作辨別，然而連專業人士亦難以分辨。安俊人力資源顧問董事總經理周綺萍經過一輪觀察，最終誤選了假證書為「真」證書；記者告知答案時，她顯得十分驚訝：「吓？唔係掛！」<br />\n<br />\n周綺萍分析，據其過往經驗，畢業證書的印章一般不會過於鮮豔，而是次真證書的印章貼近棗紅色，紙質較薄，反而假證書的紙質較厚，貼近常見證書的厚度，因而誤選。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1615165/org/cd83405f66994ead1468b2cc8eaf53cb.jpg/vp5HSbvQUD_kt1j-bN2OIjfssdXcrTPHBQjhKgUI4So?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1615165%2Forg%2Fcd83405f66994ead1468b2cc8eaf53cb.jpg%2Fvp5HSbvQUD_kt1j-bN2OIjfssdXcrTPHBQjhKgUI4So%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=db643fe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n律師莊耀洸表示，如果有人持相關假證書充當學歷證明，有機會構成刑事罪行。（鄧穎韜攝）<br />\n<br />\n港大校友、教協副會長、律師莊耀洸表示，如果有人持相關假證書充當學歷證明，相關行為有機會構成刑事罪行，觸犯「有犯罪或不誠實意圖取用電腦」、「使用虛假文書」及「欺詐罪」；當中，不誠實取用電腦罪最高刑罰為監禁5年，使用虛假文書及欺詐罪最高刑罰同樣為監禁14年。此外，若僱主在聘用僱員後發現其學歷證明屬於虛假，可以根據《僱傭條例》，以「犯有欺詐或不忠實行為」理由，無須給予通知或代通知金，終止僱傭合約。<br />\n<br />\n就相關假證書事宜，香港大學發言人回應《香港01》查詢時指出，港大每年均接獲有關學歷確認的查詢，包括確認畢業證書是否由港大發出；港大畢業證書有防偽特徵，過去多年曾揭發過極少數偽造港大畢業證書的個案，並按照個別情況，採取了適當的行動。"},{"pid":"8242b610030e25e58c1f81018b57547a5561b784","tid":735122,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:40:16.000Z","msg":"正常公司會check學歷"},{"pid":"01a147d293917d0e0610583fc4e0b6744c7082b8","tid":735122,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:40:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://scd.cn.rfi.fr/sites/chinese.filesrfi/imagecache/rfi_16x9_1024_578/sites/images.rfi.fr/files/aef_image/btjb-fyrwsqi0767868.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscd.cn.rfi.fr%2Fsites%2Fchinese.filesrfi%2Fimagecache%2Frfi_16x9_1024_578%2Fsites%2Fimages.rfi.fr%2Ffiles%2Faef_image%2Fbtjb-fyrwsqi0767868.png&h=b09c5666&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2dd94a86a48d1b8547a4f162d37d150fa8008edf","tid":735122,"uid":149844,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:42:26.000Z","msg":"連證書都有得造假CLS"},{"pid":"20865612d708c221040944598c2ad8351f897231","tid":735122,"uid":98386,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:47:20.000Z","msg":"周屎萍呢啲垃圾身居高位連真假證書都未識分 仲成撚日死出黎話年輕人心頭高唔肯捱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4302a45508a519d3286f333438f301319137f7","tid":735122,"uid":46328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:48:57.000Z","msg":"鄧 幾廿萬讀張野返黎個d人唔抵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51441e90869800b36f4c59ef890f74ed1eb0e6f3","tid":735122,"uid":55597,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:50:54.000Z","msg":"周綺萍平時抽新人水<br />\n而家比份真假辨認都做唔到，搵佢就 hr 守關就死得<br />\n隨時請個賊返工"},{"pid":"7e47dce466b63c020419ceb79c529900178c466a","tid":735122,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:51:07.000Z","msg":"蘇文大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d946e6f0f729e02f7499a4be75db0473f4594249","tid":735122,"uid":46328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"51441e90869800b36f4c59ef890f74ed1eb0e6f3","tid":735122,"uid":55597,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:50:54.000Z","msg":"周綺萍平時抽新人水<br />\n而家比份真假辨認都做唔到，搵佢就 hr 守關就死得<br />\n隨時請個賊返工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:51:12.000Z","msg":"我就咁睇相都分到真假<br />\n資深人力資源顧問食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> [fuck]"},{"pid":"eb66c727cdb0eaeec7e501670ad5b2a9b6464402","tid":735122,"uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"788f4fce0bf4cf9b162594b448948bc2b6bba496","tid":735122,"uid":46328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:38:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1623392/org/e4bc74ad4bc4bf58c16d569c5066c38a.jpg/e_acOd00PtJKr_tA50iDTn49ne15q_38zyxCRM8sQkQ?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1623392%2Forg%2Fe4bc74ad4bc4bf58c16d569c5066c38a.jpg%2Fe_acOd00PtJKr_tA50iDTn49ne15q_38zyxCRM8sQkQ%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=f96afe6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n資深人力資源顧問周綺萍誤選了假證書為「真」證書，記者告知答案時，她顯得十分驚訝。（王海圖攝）<br />\n<br />\n資深人力顧問錯選假證書：紙質較厚<br />\n<br />\n內地網售虛假港大證書有幾真？記者帶同真假證書，分別找到人力資源顧問及律師作辨別，然而連專業人士亦難以分辨。安俊人力資源顧問董事總經理周綺萍經過一輪觀察，最終誤選了假證書為「真」證書；記者告知答案時，她顯得十分驚訝：「吓？唔係掛！」<br />\n<br />\n周綺萍分析，據其過往經驗，畢業證書的印章一般不會過於鮮豔，而是次真證書的印章貼近棗紅色，紙質較薄，反而假證書的紙質較厚，貼近常見證書的厚度，因而誤選。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1615165/org/cd83405f66994ead1468b2cc8eaf53cb.jpg/vp5HSbvQUD_kt1j-bN2OIjfssdXcrTPHBQjhKgUI4So?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1615165%2Forg%2Fcd83405f66994ead1468b2cc8eaf53cb.jpg%2Fvp5HSbvQUD_kt1j-bN2OIjfssdXcrTPHBQjhKgUI4So%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=db643fe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n律師莊耀洸表示，如果有人持相關假證書充當學歷證明，有機會構成刑事罪行。（鄧穎韜攝）<br />\n<br />\n港大校友、教協副會長、律師莊耀洸表示，如果有人持相關假證書充當學歷證明，相關行為有機會構成刑事罪行，觸犯「有犯罪或不誠實意圖取用電腦」、「使用虛假文書」及「欺詐罪」；當中，不誠實取用電腦罪最高刑罰為監禁5年，使用虛假文書及欺詐罪最高刑罰同樣為監禁14年。此外，若僱主在聘用僱員後發現其學歷證明屬於虛假，可以根據《僱傭條例》，以「犯有欺詐或不忠實行為」理由，無須給予通知或代通知金，終止僱傭合約。<br />\n<br />\n就相關假證書事宜，香港大學發言人回應《香港01》查詢時指出，港大每年均接獲有關學歷確認的查詢，包括確認畢業證書是否由港大發出；港大畢業證書有防偽特徵，過去多年曾揭發過極少數偽造港大畢業證書的個案，並按照個別情況，採取了適當的行動。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:51:40.000Z","msg":"HR咁樣做野，炒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e24317332b0feea253b6750957fd61b66147676","tid":735122,"uid":113000,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:58:50.000Z","msg":"周綺萍 條打手證書都唔識睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1727fbe9b96678341dcd0c10becfac4ecd2ffeb","tid":735122,"uid":10692,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T09:02:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f2f6b5736d9e86f504ae8cdb04bd90a94fcd069b","tid":735122,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T09:03:25.000Z","msg":"Donald Tsang <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做假都唔該做認真少少啦"},{"pid":"625cca75a97c0eaf9aaa28b8345544562ef6b340","tid":735122,"uid":181747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T09:05:18.000Z","msg":"港大張證書係好撚薄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 流到"},{"pid":"f60eac492bd9e1ee0e9859d8f6d55b3d83a350d0","tid":735122,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T09:07:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">傾多2句都知假<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/a